      "span_text": "In this paper, we are concerned with the initial-value problem associated with the generalized periodic Camassa-Holm (µCH) equation       µ(u t ) − u xxt = −2µ(u)u x + 2u x u xx + uu xxx , t > 0, x ∈ R, u(0, x) = u 0 (x), x ∈ R, u(t, x + 1) = u(t, x), t ≥ 0, x ∈ R,",
